metadata.name: Exposed Soul
metadata.description:
Size: 4724*7087PX / 27MB

If we regard the changes in the soul as changes in human appearance, then human appearance will constantly change with the changes in the soul. This change may cause people to change their understanding of their own appearance, or affect their perception of other humans. In this case, the skin of the viewer may also change with the changes in the soul. Perhaps our understanding of others is also our own self-awareness.
